item.title: I just need help just litterely running up the client i
item.dc:creator: @i_want_fire i want fire
item.description:
@i_want_fire wrote:

When you download a client+source you like then just open both of them and click where it says “run” a cmd should pop up for the source and for the client a cmd and a runescape client should pop up. Then the cache should auto-download if not then download the cache where you downloaded the client+source and put it in your “c-drive” and then run your source and client. Thing to note: Make sure you have jdk so that if the run of the source and it’s not the right version that you change it to your version of jdk. This is the most basic information of an rsps so good luck.
